My app should let users:

Create events
Invite people
Manage attendees
Track event details
View upcoming events
RSVP to events
Think of it like a flexible event organizer where users decide what kind of event they want to manage.

Examples:

Birthday party
Wedding function
College event
Meetup
House party
Office gathering
Club event
Community event

MVP Features
**User Features

Sign up
Log in
Log out
Edit profile


**Event Features
Create event
Edit event
Delete event
View event details
View all events created by the user
View upcoming events
Event Fields


